B.Mm=new A.pa("case1","Case 1: Motor Neuron Disease","A 55-year-old male presenting with progressive, painless, asymmetric limb weakness and visible twitching in his arms.","Abundant (3+) fibrillations and PSWs in three limbs, extremely large duration and high-amplitude polyphasic MUAPs, profoundly reduced recruitment, and frequent fasciculations.",B.a3Z)
