B.MZ=new A.cv("The Rule","Normal MUAPs have 2-4 phases. >4 phases is considered polyphasic.")
B.MG=new A.cv("The Standard","Up to 10% of MUAPs can be polyphasic in completely healthy muscle. Don't overcall it.")
B.N2=new A.cv("The Sound","A higher-frequency, somewhat 'clicky' or 'scratchy' sound due to the rapid baseline crossings.")
B.MR=new A.cv("The Significance","It is simply a measure of desynchronization. It does NOT distinguish between neuropathy and myopathy.")
