c1=A.a([A.Y(ac7,d9),A.Y("Large Fiber Polyneuropathy","Large fiber involvement would typically show abnormal vibration/proprioception, absent reflexes, and abnormal NCS (low amplitudes or slow velocities); here all are normal."),A.Y("Erythromelalgia","Characterized by episodic redness and warmth in addition to burning pain; here there are no visible skin changes or color changes."),A.Y(ac8,"Pain is typically worse with the first steps in the morning and localized to the calcaneal insertion; here it is diffuse, burning, and nocturnal."),A.Y("L5-S1 Radiculopathy","Would be asymmetric, usually involve back pain, and often show reflex/strength changes; here it is symmetric and distal.")],ae9)
